Name: Multimirror
About the game: Multimirror is a minimal grid-based puzzle game. Reflect circles around other circles and take the red circle to the winning point! Features: 50 handcrafted levels Random level generator with adjustable size and difficulty. Full-fledged level-editor Create and share your own levels or random levels you generate, and discover brain-melting levels crafted by the community! Achievements, trading cards, cloud saves
